snippet: Jets Coach Rex Ryan acknowledged discussing Ed Reed, who became a free agent on Wednesday after clearing waivers, with General Manager John Idzik, but it is unclear whether there will be a reunion.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Jets coach Rex Ryan acknowledges that team has discussed re-signing safety Ed Reed, who has become a free agent; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jets Coach Rex Ryan acknowledged discussing Ed Reed, who became a free agent on Wednesday after clearing waivers, with General Manager John Idzik, but it is unclear whether there will be a reunion.

headline.main: Jets Consider Adding Reed at Safety
headline.print_headline: Jets Consider Adding Reed At Safety
